[
    {
        "content": "<p>Is there a reason <code>division_ring α</code> isn't defined as <code>extends ring α, group_with_zero α.</code>?</p>",
        "id": 217880233,
        "sender_full_name": "Anne Baanen",
        "timestamp": 1606308923
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Seems like a good idea to me</p>",
        "id": 217880587,
        "sender_full_name": "Eric Wieser",
        "timestamp": 1606309095
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>the reason is of course that division rings were there in 2017 and that nobody is interested in them</p>",
        "id": 217880699,
        "sender_full_name": "Kevin Buzzard",
        "timestamp": 1606309157
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>and group_with_zeros were only there in 2019 or maybe 2020</p>",
        "id": 217880733,
        "sender_full_name": "Kevin Buzzard",
        "timestamp": 1606309177
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Also I think you can then remove the <code>inv_mul_cancel</code> field from <code>division_ring</code></p>",
        "id": 217880745,
        "sender_full_name": "Eric Wieser",
        "timestamp": 1606309188
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Since <code>group_with_zero</code> derives that for you</p>",
        "id": 217880761,
        "sender_full_name": "Eric Wieser",
        "timestamp": 1606309197
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Do you end up with two multiplications if you extend ring and group_with_zero? Oh you use old structure command I guess</p>",
        "id": 217880823,
        "sender_full_name": "Kevin Buzzard",
        "timestamp": 1606309212
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>you can't use old structure command on stuff which has been made with new structure command, so this might be an issue</p>",
        "id": 217880854,
        "sender_full_name": "Kevin Buzzard",
        "timestamp": 1606309237
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><code>division_ring</code> and <code>group_with_zero</code> are old structures</p>",
        "id": 217880921,
        "sender_full_name": "Anne Baanen",
        "timestamp": 1606309271
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I think there was a push to remove redundant axioms at one point that made this definition not suitable</p>",
        "id": 217880981,
        "sender_full_name": "Mario Carneiro",
        "timestamp": 1606309304
    },
    {
